:INFO
About Draftkit
Draftkit is a distraction-free writing and publishing toolkit for bloggers, newsletter writers,
and indie content creators. Write in Markdown, publish to your own domain, and reach your audience
directly — no middleman, no subscription, no algorithm deciding your reach.

Available on macOS, Windows, and the web. One-time purchase, yours forever.
|
:COUNTER.half
3 Platforms Supported
|
:COUNTER.half
$49 One-Time Price


