:INFO
The Story
Draftkit started as a personal tool Alex built for his own newsletter in 2019. After sharing it
with a few writer friends, it grew quietly by word of mouth for two years before a Product Hunt
launch in 2021 pushed it to 1 000 users overnight. Version 2.0 is the first major rethink of
the product since that launch.
|
:COUNTER.half
5 Years in Development


